data.meta_description: 4,126 likes, 116 comments - imomsohard on January 8, 2024: "We were born and raised in Nebraska, but we’ve been living in California for a while so we’ve lost our winter coat.  Basically we are giant babies in the cold now.  Enjoy this blast from the past and all of your moms who are dealing with the cold our hats are off to you (but not for too long because we get chilly). #midwest #moms #tough #nice #midwestnice #minnesota #nebraska #illinois #ohio #northdakota #southdakota #coldplaces #bestpeople #happynewyear #throwback #hotchocolate #morehotchocolate".
